P(X = 9) = C(10,9) × (0.7)⁹ × (0.3)¹
= 10 × 0.040353607 × 0.3
= 10 × 0.012106082
= 0.12106082

P(X = 10) = C(10,10) × (0.7)¹⁰ × (0.3)⁰
= 1 × 0.028247953 × 1
= 0.028247953

P(X ≥ 9) = 0.12106082 + 0.028247953 = 0.149308773

P(X ≤ 8) = 1 - 0.149308773 = 0.850691227

**Computing P(max ≥ 9):**

P(max ≤ 8) = (0.850691227)³ = 0.614779156

P(max ≥ 9) = 1 - 0.614779156 = 0.385220844

Rounding to 4 significant figures: 0.3852

