- P(W|B₂) = 0/2 = 0
- P(W|B₃) = 2/4 = 1/2
- P(W|B₄) = 3/4

**Apply the law of total probability:**

P(W) = P(W|B₁)·P(B₁) + P(W|B₂)·P(B₂) + P(W|B₃)·P(B₃) + P(W|B₄)·P(B₄)

